overview: Ariel (Juliana Kincaid) is warming up to the lifestyle of a glamour model, and mega-hunk Lance is warming up to her. But is the lust and easy virtue of lingerie modeling just too much for a simple girl from a small town? And is her cousin Tracy (Diana Espen) really as supportive as she appears? What scheme is she cooking up with her boy-toy lackey?  Meanwhile, Bobby continues to sample the pleasures of Lust Angeles, including his dominatrix-by-nigth neighbor (Angela Nicholas). But when Bobby tries to run his own little corer of the sex industry, he finds out that women need it just as bad as men - and they're willing to pay!
title: Dirty Angels 3: Model Behavior
